data.description: Located in the heart of the historic Carriage Town neighborhood, blocks from downtown amenities, this home offers the chance to own a home in an area undergoing remarkable revitalization. Completely remodeled in 2011 including all plumbing, electrical, roof, furnace, water heater, windows and the entire interior, you can enjoy the historic appeal of the neighborhood without the stress and maintenance of a 100 year old home. Complete with a large front porch to sit out and enjoy those summer days, a private backyard, natural wood floors, first floor bedroom with private bath and another full bath upstairs with laundry facilities so you don't have to go down to the basement to do laundry!
